[QuickStartCard]
Content = """
OPERATOR QUICK-START CARD (v1.0)

[Core Commands]
status      → System status
mesh        → Planetary mesh view
basins      → Basin map
arcs        → Arc map
topology    → System topology
pressure    → Pressure map
density     → Density map
coherence   → Coherence report
global      → Global view

[Diagnostics]
- Run drift check: diagnostics.drift
- Run contamination check: diagnostics.contamination
- Run integrity scan: diagnostics.integrity

[Stability]
- Check turbulence: stability.turbulence
- Check pressure: stability.pressure
- Check operator state: stability.operator

[Propagation]
- View message map: propagation.messages
- View translation map: propagation.translation

[Mesh]
- Global flows: mesh.flows
- Cross-scale dynamics: mesh.crossscale
- Hydronic weather: mesh.weather
- Planetary diagnostics: mesh.diagnostics

[Operator Notes]
- Maintain laminar state
- Use diagnostics before intervention
- Mesh is self-correcting under normal load
"""
